title: Isms
body:
Listen up writers of Fanfic. Pay attention to your canon.

Not regarding ships.

I’m talking about isms. If a fandom is British - such as Harry Potter, then please, please, please don’t make the characters sound like they’re from New York.

Having said that, if your fandom is US based - such as Teen Wolf, then for the love of the goddess, don’t have them using shall and offering to make endless cups of tea!
